rso, a Escola de Saúde da UFRN há perspectiva de abrir uma nova turma em 2019.1, e que estão nos momentos iniciais de elaboração de edital do processo seletivo.</p><p><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/DSCN0075.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7141\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/DSCN0075.jpg\" alt=\"dscn0075\" width=\"5184\" height=\"3888\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8184.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7142\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8184.jpg\" alt=\"img_8184\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8203.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7143\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8203.jpg\" alt=\"img_8203\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8300.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7144\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8300.jpg\" alt=\"img_8300\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8360.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7145\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8360.jpg\" alt=\"img_8360\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8464.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7146\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8464.jpg\" alt=\"img_8464\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8602.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7147\" src=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8602.jpg\" alt=\"img_8602\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" /></a><a href=\"http://escoladesaude.ufrn.br/wp-content/uploads/IMG_8625.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-714